[00:00] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'Drones revolutionized the way we capture action sports, but one environment always remained off limits. Water. Until now. Hover Air Aqua is the world\'s first 100% waterproof self-flying action'

[00:13] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'camera designed for life on the water. It floats, follows, and films you automatically. No controller, no phone, and no bulky setup. No more begging for your friends to get the shot. Aqua is as'

[00:27] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'simple as it gets. Choose a flight mode, toss it in the water, and tap a button to launch. From there, smart AI tracking keeps you perfectly in frame. [Music]'

[00:40] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'Aqua powers through level seven winds and keeps up with you on your favorite activities at speeds up to 55 km an hour. Aqua lets you focus on doing what you love, not on how to capture it. What'

[00:54] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'are you waiting for? Time to make a splash. [Music]'
